<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>흐늘흐늘하다 [흐늘흐늘하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. soft; wavy; floaty</dd><br>
<dd>힘없이 늘어져 자꾸 흔들릴 정도로 가볍고 부드럽다.</dd><br>
<dd>Light and soft to the extent of drooping feebly and swaying repeatedly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. spongy; pulpy; squashy</dd><br>
<dd>물체가 자꾸 뭉크러지거나 흔들릴 정도로 단단하지 못하다.</dd><br>
<dd>An object being soft-textured so that it keeps swaying or cannot hold its shape.</dd><br>
<dt>푹신하다 [푹씬하다]</dt><br>
<dd>soft; spongy; pillowy</dd><br>
<dd>조금 푸근하게 부드럽고 탄력이 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling soft and elastic, slightly comfortable.</dd><br>
<dt>푹신푹신하다 [푹씬푹씬하다]</dt><br>
<dd>soft; snug; comfortable</dd><br>
<dd>매우 푸근하게 부드럽고 탄력이 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling soft and elastic, in a very snug way.</dd><br>
<dt>푸근하다 [푸근하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. cozy; snug; soft</dd><br>
<dd>꽤 두꺼운 물건이나 자리가 부드럽고 따뜻하다.</dd><br>
<dd>A substantially thick object or seat being soft and warm.</dd><br>
<dd>2. comfortable</dd><br>
<dd>느낌이나 분위기가 부드럽고 따뜻하여 편안하다.</dd><br>
<dd>A feeling or atmosphere that is comfortable because it is soft and warm.</dd><br>
<dd>3. warm</dd><br>
<dd>날씨가 바람이 없고 꽤 따뜻하다.</dd><br>
<dd>The weather being windless and quite warm.</dd><br>
<dt>폭신하다 [폭씬하다]</dt><br>
